OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe north fading as cloudier
OL,7,Fconditions extend southwards, perhaps
OL,8,Fsome fog patches forming in any
OL,9,Fclearer breaks ahead of this. Light
OL,10,Fwinds. Feeling cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter
OL,13,Fwith warm sunny spells developing and
OL,14,Falso scattered afternoon showers,
OL,15,Fthese locally heavy with a low chance
OL,16,Fof thunder. Winds remaining generally
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
