OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,7,Fshowers each day, these perhaps more
OL,8,Flikely Tuesday. Turning cooler, with
OL,9,Fovernight rural grass frost possible
OL,10,Fin sheltered spots. Winds mostly light.
